~~ Executable register-only slice of particles_400_run.rk.
~~
~~ Each parameter is one target-native rack. The surrounding pack traversal is
~~ deliberately absent because native `run`/`over` lowering is not available
~~ yet; the current AVX2 backend can compile and verify this straight-line body.
crunch advance_x(position_x: f32s, velocity_x: f32s, <dt: f32>) -> f32s:
  | displacement: f32s <| velocity_x * <dt>
  | result: f32s <| position_x + displacement
  return result
